rovide a model Hamiltonian for the\ntopological nematic states that have not been realized numerically.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 30 Aug 2013 19:49:47 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 3 Sep 2014 15:47:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-09-04"}
