t the majority of warm\nJupiters with low-e (e <~0.2) are not misaligned, in contrast with low-e hot\nJupiters.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 30 Aug 2013 20:00:18 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 3 Dec 2013 05:46:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-12-25"}
