ich QSi(C) can be easily determined, and another condition\nsuch that PSi can be broken into disjoint pieces that can be minimized\nseparately.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 30 Aug 2013 21:14:26 GMT"},{"version":"v10","created":"Thu, 31 Jul 2014 11:49:28 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 19 Oct 2013 20:44:10 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 18 Nov 2013 16:48:35 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Fri, 28 Feb 2014 14:45:07 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Wed, 9 Apr 2014 20:49:13 GMT"},{"version":"v6","created":"Tue, 3 Jun 2014 13:48:07 GMT"},{"version":"v7","created":"Wed, 4 Jun 2014 19:54:49 GMT"},{"version":"v8","created":"Wed, 23 Jul 2014 21:32:13 GMT"},{"version":"v9","created":"Wed, 30 Jul 2014 14:15:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-08-01"}
